#' Extract Uncorrelated Posterior Samples
#'
#' This function extracts uncorrelated posterior samples of an outbreak.
#'
#' @param results MCMC output as generated by run_mcmc.
#' @param burnin We discard the first (burnin * 100) percent of the results
#' @return An uncorrelated Markov chain, of the same format as the "results" input.
#' @export

